    "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"nofollow\" />\n<title>leetMX - Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</title>\n<link href=\"/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n</head>\n<body class=\"mbody\">\n<div class=\"logos\">\n<table border=\"0\"><tr><td><a href=\"https://www.etda.or.th\"><img src=\"/img/logo-etda.png\" height=\"50\" alt=\"ETDA\" title=\"Visit the ETDA website\" /></a></td>\n<td><font size=\"3\">สำนักงานพัฒนาธุรกรรมทางอิเล็กทรอนิกส์<br />Electronic Transactions Development Agency</font></td></tr></table>\n</div>\n<link href=\"/menubar.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<div id=\"menubar\">\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\">Groups</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listtools.cgi\">Tools</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\">Search</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptstats.cgi\">Statistics</a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"graph\">\n<div class=\"gline\"><img src=\"/img/clear.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"3\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div><img src=\"/img/report.jpg\" width=\"900\" alt=\"Report\" /></div>\n<a name=\"top\"></a>\n<div class=\"searchdiv\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\" title=\"Search the database\" class=\"inlink\">Search</a></div>\n<div class=\"outermain\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"Home\">Home</a> &gt; <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"List all groups\">List all groups</a> &gt; leetMX</div>\n<h1>Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</h1>\n<div class=\"innermainov\">\n<h3><a href=\"/cgi-bin/showcard.cgi?u=e8fab0e1-c3e1-4d53-bcf7-614c18ca665c\" title=\"Get permanent link to this card\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/link.png\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Permanent link\" /></a> APT group: leetMX</h3>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">leetMX <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Country</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?c=Mexico\" title=\"Search for all threat groups from Mexico\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/flags/Mexico.png\" alt=\"Mexico\" width=\"33\" height=\"20\" /> Mexico</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Motivation</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?m=Information%20theft%20and%20espionage\" title=\"Search for all threat groups with motivation Information theft and espionage\" class=\"inlink\">Information theft and espionage</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">First seen</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">2016</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Description</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">",
    "leetMX is a widespread cyber-attack campaign originating from Mexico and focused on targets in Mexico, El Salvador, and other countries in Latin America, such as Guatemala, Argentina and Costa Rica. It has been operating since November 2016 at least. We are uncertain of its objectives but estimate it is criminally motivated.<br /><br />leetMX infrastructure includes 27 hosts and domains used for malware delivery or for command and control.  Hundreds of malware samples have been used, most are Remote Access Trojans and keyloggers.<br /><br />Interestingly, the attackers camouflage one of their delivery domains by redirecting visitors to El Universal, a major Mexican newspaper.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Countries: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Argentina\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Argentina\" class=\"inlink\">Argentina</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Costa%20Rica\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Costa Rica\" class=\"inlink\">Costa Rica</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=El%20Salvador\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target El Salvador\" class=\"inlink\">El Salvador</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Guatemala\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Guatemala\" class=\"inlink\">Guatemala</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Mexico\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Mexico\" class=\"inlink\">Mexico</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=USA\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target USA\" class=\"inlink\">USA</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Tools used</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Information</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://www.clearskysec.com/leetmx/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.clearskysec.com/leetmx/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 29 April 2020</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=leetMX&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=leetMX&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Facebook\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/etda_thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-twitter.png\" alt=\"Twitter\" title=\"Follow us on Twitter\" /></a>\n</td><td colspan=\"2\">\n<h3>Report incidents</h3>\n</td>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"0%\"><img src=\"/img/icon-phone.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\" /></td>\n<td width=\"20%\"><strong>+66"
